(1, 'Dr. Bhawna Attri', '<p>Dr. Bhawna Attri is a renowned endocrinologist dedicated to providing exceptional care to her patients in South Delhi. With a stellar educational background from prestigious institutions including AIIMS and MAMC, Dr. Attri brings a wealth of knowledge and expertise to her practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specializing in a comprehensive range of endocrine disorders, Dr. Attri offers diagnosis and management for conditions such as diabetes, obesity, thyroid disorders, and more. Her commitment to advancing the field is reflected in her prolific research and contributions to reputable medical journals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beyond her credentials, Dr. Attri is known for her compassionate approach and dedication to improving the health and well-being of her patients. Whether you&#39;re seeking treatment for a common endocrine disorder or a complex condition, Dr. Attri&#39;s personalized care and clinical excellence ensure that you receive the highest quality of treatment and support. Trust your endocrine health to Dr. Bhawna Attri and experience the difference that expertise and compassion can make.</p>', '<h3><strong>Discover Excellence in Endocrine Care</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Dr. Bhawna Attri&#39;s Endocrinology Clinic, where exceptional care meets expertise. Dr. Attri, a distinguished endocrinologist, brings her unparalleled skills and compassionate approach to address a wide range of endocrine disorders. With a commitment to advancing the field through research and evidence-based practices, Dr. Attri stands as a beacon of quality care in South Delhi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore our services, learn about Dr. Attri&#39;s background, and discover why patients trust her as their partner in health. Whether you&#39;re seeking treatment for diabetes, thyroid disorders, or other endocrine conditions, you&#39;re in capable hands at our clinic. Experience the difference that personalized care and expertise can make in your journey to better health.</p>', 'dr_bhawnaAttri.jpeg', 'Dr. Bhawna Attri', '+918810674844', 'bmkk88@gmail.com', 'E-29 Amar Medical Centre, near Pramod Mahajan Marg, Block E, Saket, South Delhi, New  Delhi,', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3505.6074212391354!2d77.20131678093978!3d28.521456813135586!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390cdd13aa15d1df%3A0xf01b547a6f6916ec!2sDr.%20Bhawna%20Attri-%20Best%20Endocrinologist%20Doctor%20in%20South%20Delhi%20(Obesity%2C%20Thyroid%20and%20Diabetes%20Specialist%20in%20Delhi)!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1712578517334!5m2!1sen!2sin\" width=\"100%\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', 1);

