-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2018 &ndash; Doctor of Medicine (M.D), General Medicine, Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sciences</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2013 - Bachelor of Medicine, Bachelor of Surgery (M.B.B.S), Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose Medical College, Subharti University</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2008 - Class XII, CBSE, Delhi Public School, Vasant Kunj, Delhi</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:17pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><strong>Research and Thesis</strong></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2024 &ndash; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><em>Young Stroke: An Eagle Eye View</em></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2023 &ndash; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><em>Unusual PSA uptake in seronegative paraneoplastic brainstem encephalitis: A case report</em></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2021 &ndash; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><em>An Observational Cross-sectional Study to assess Autonomic Nervous System dysfunction in Irritable Bowel Syndrome</em></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">2017 - </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><em>Clinical Correlation of serum Uric Acid and Lipid profile in Acute Cerebrovascular events with Radiological Studies in JJM Medical College, Davangere</em></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:17pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><strong>Professional Affiliations and Licensure</strong></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">Delhi Medical Council, India DMC/R/10902</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:17pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\"><strong>Conferences and Workshops</strong></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">November 2021 &ndash; Second position in Stroke Quiz by Apollo Hospital, Delhi</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">August 2022 &ndash; Participated in Neurophysiology Workshop at World Neurosciences Summit</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">Online &ndash; Paper presentation on Rhino-oculo-cerebral mucormycosis during COVID-19 at Sir Ganga Ram Hospital-Harvard Medical School Meet</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'dr_bharat', 'Dr. Bharat Rastogi Neurologist', 'Neurologist', 'Dr. Bharat Rastogi Neurologist', 1),
(13, 'DR. SHREYA GOEL', ' Obstetrics and Gynaecology', '419572996_sheeya.png', '<p><span style=\"font-size:36pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>DR. SHREYA GOEL</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Specialties:</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;Obstetrics and Gynaecology, Fetal Medicine</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Education:</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Diplomat of National Board (D.N.B) in Obstetrics and Gynaecology, 2023</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Master of Surgery (M.S) in Obstetrics and Gynaecology, Lady Hardinge Medical College, 2021</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Bachelor of Medicine, Bachelor of Surgery (M.B.B.S), Lady Hardinge Medical College, 2017</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Class XII, CBSE, Delhi Public School, R.K Puram, Delhi, 2011</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Class X, CBSE, Convent of Jesus and Mary, Delhi, 2009</span></span></s